data.description: Come home to the highly desirable Summerset 1 community. This beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bath, move in ready home is located in a gated 55+ senior community with a pool, tennis courts, bocce courts, a fitness center and many organized activities. The home has been freshly painted and has new carpet in the bedrooms. It features separate living and family rooms, an eat in kitchen and dining area. Both rooms have walk in closets. The home is located close to shopping, medical centers and dining facilities.  Also close to Hwy 4 for easy travels to other areas.
